<i>
Wed, 12 Aug 92 14:47:43 BST
</i><PRE>

                              [... Jonathan sent in a bunch of further stuff 
                              on this topic, excised for brevity.  PGN]

Last night's ITN 10 o'clock news was rather more sensationalist, showing a
