&gt;Date:         Tue, 23 Feb 1993 22:55:18 GMT
&gt;Sender:       Computers and Society ARPA Digest &lt;COMSOC-L@AUVM.BITNET&gt;
&gt;From:         Shellie Emmons &lt;sme46782@uxa.cso.uiuc.edu&gt;
