&gt;the following:
&gt;
&gt;  (1)  When you get thousands of messages a day, how do you
&gt;       respond effectively?
&gt;  (2)  How do you make a public e-mail system inclusive
&gt;       and accessible?
&gt;  (3)  What would happen if e-mail became the primary
&gt;       mode of(mediated) access to government?
&gt;
